      <h1 id="headline" class="headline-font text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold leading-tight mb-4" style="color: #ffffff;">Seravell Summit Concludes with Landmark Economic and Security Pact</h1><!-- Subheadline -->
      <p id="subheadline" class="body-font text-xl md:text-2xl leading-relaxed mb-8" style="color: #b0b0c0;">GHXE, Crossia, and San Caelora announce tariff liberalization, six-month defense framework, and establishment of Arsenic Trade Organization</p><!-- Byline -->
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 pb-8 mb-8 border-b" style="border-color: #2a2a35;">
